Gemini said


*Scale Your Brand with our Infrastructure*





Many businesses and vendors lose out on projects because they lack the
in-house product and services to handle the workload. We provide a
*whitelabeled application* that allows you to offer a professional,
brand-forward solution, including multi-language support. This allows the
brands to deliver a world-class services under their own theme and logo.


What Will you Get?


We are whitelabeling our Admin App which provides you with all these
features:

   -

   *Unified Landing Page:* Access a holistic view of your brand with
   accurate data on Trips, revenue, and scanning in one place.
   -

   *Flexible Order Management:* Easily manage your workflow by inwarding
   anything from single shipments to multiple bulk orders instantly.
   -

   *Manage Riders:* Monitor your riders by keeping track of their
   attendence, location, leaves and much more.
   -

   *Cash Management:* Streamline your finances with built-in tools to
   manage your cash flow and COD (Cash on Delivery) settlements directly.


Why It=E2=80=99s Good for you!

This service allows you to scale your business instantly without incurring

a massive capital investment, executed in a brand centric manner.
What=E2=80=99s Next

Something exciting is coming soon - Stay tuned !!
